title: Quest Virtual Care
description: Quest Diagnostics leverages 98point6 and SteadyMD to deliver virtual care. The Quest Virtual Care app combines the expertise of SteadyMD’s US board-certified providers with the power of 98point6 artificial intelligence to deliver virtual care via private and secure in-app messaging. Quest Virtual Care allows users to ask their clinical care team questions about their screening results and receive personalized health management guidance. The clinical care team can provide treatment recommendations, order follow-up testing, prescribe medications, and even help with acute conditions that may arise.
